name: HEN 2021 Frame Sheet Dispensing Bobbin
description:
Document of HEN 2021 Frame Sheet Dispensing Bobbin. 
Holds roughly 14 yards of frame sheet or 168 frames (100mm wxh). This objkt is to be distributed to every wallet that, in the year 2021, collected a non-fungible token created by Huw Messie via hicetnunc, objkt.com, or fxhash.xyz. Created by Huw Messie 2022 (Twitter,TikTok: @huwythechew, IG: @huwmessie). BLACK DENIM, WHITE DENIM, 22 INCH BLACK PURSE ZIPPER, TANGO RED FAUX SUEDE, MEDIEVAL BLUE FAUX SUEDE, CLEAR VINYL, BLACK, RED POLYESTER THREAD.
